    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A burst of cold energy emanates from you in a 30-foot cone. Each creature in that area must make a Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, a creature takes [[/r 3d8]] cold damage and is hindered by ice formations for 1 minute, or until it or another creature within reach of it uses an action to break away the ice. A creature hindered by ice has its speed reduced to 0. On a successful save, a creature takes half as much damage and isnt hindered by ice.</p><h3>At Higher Levels</h3><p>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, increase the cold damage by [[/r 1d8]] for each slot level above 2nd.</p><p><strong>Spell Lists.</strong> Sorcerer, Wizard</p>",
